    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      68.0,
      164.5,
      310.51,
      189.97
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka as follows: -",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      68.0,
      200.34,
      310.5,
      225.97
    ],
    "text": "1. (1) This Act may be cited as the Budgetary Relief Allowance of Workers (Amendment) Act, No.10 of 2025.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      68.0,
      236.5,
      310.51,
      261.97
    ],
    "text": "(2) The provisions of this Act shall be deemed to have come into operation on April 1, 2025.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      68.0,
      272.34,
      310.49,
      297.97
    ],
    "text": "2. Section 3 of the Budgetary Relief Allowance of Workers Act, No. 4 of 2016 is hereby amended as follows: -",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      92.0,
      308.5,
      310.51,
      369.97
    ],
    "text": "(1) in subsection (1) thereof, by the substitution for the words and figures \"With effect from May 1, 2015,\", of the words and figures \"For the period commencing on May 1, 2015 and ending on March 31, 2025, ''; and",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      92.0,
      380.5,
      310.52,
      441.97
    ],
    "text": "(2) in subsection (2) thereof, by the substitution for the words and figures \"commencing from January 1, 2016\", of the words and figures \"for the period commencing on January 1, 2016 and ending on March 31, 2025,\".",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      68.0,
      452.34,
      310.49,
      489.97
    ],
    "text": "3. In the event of any inconsistency between the Sinhala and Tamil texts of this Act, the Sinhala text shall prevail.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
